* Advanced Programmable Interrupt Controller (APIC)
* Inter-processor interrupt (IPI)
* Interrupt latency
* Interrupts in 65xx processors
* IRQL (Windows)
* Non-maskable interrupt (NMI)
* Programmable Interrupt Controller (PIC)
* Red zone
