<doc id="638835" wikidata="Q783438" url="?curid=638835" title="Hotot-en-Auge">
<text>Hotot-en-Auge (, literally &quot;Hotot in Auge&quot;) is a commune in the Calvados department in the Normandy region in northwestern France. It is the namesake of the Dwarf Hotot and Blanc de Hotot breeds of Rabbit

==Demographics==
In 2018, the commune had 297 inhabitants.


==See also==
*Communes of the Calvados department

