<doc id="638843" wikidata="Q845366" url="?curid=638843" title="Hubert-Folie">
<text>Hubert-Folie () is a former commune in the Calvados department in the Normandy region in northwestern France. On 1 January 2019, it was merged into the new commune Castine-en-Plaine.

==Population==
==See also==
*Communes of the Calvados department

